---
title: Chicken Sausage Cottage Pie topped with Cheesy Thyme Mashed Potatoes
description: There’s nothing better than comforting classics that warm you from the inside out. Enter: our chefs’ ode to the classic cottage pie. The base is a rich, tomatoey pork sausage filling chock-full of fresh veggies and herbs. On top, swoops of creamy, thyme-flecked mashed potatoes, sprinkled with white cheddar, then broiled to create an irresistible crust.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6304e6e97798c50fef06f95c-465bdc8c.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/65e8b9fdad357710d5d54f9e.pdf
servings: 2
time required: 50 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/chicken-sausage-cottage-pie-65e8b9fdad357710d5d54f9e
author: HelloFresh
cuisine: European
nutrition:
  calories: 820 kcal
